These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: mexican, egyptian, chinese, nigerian
1. Nationality:egyptian is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:nigerian is between Nationality:mexican and Nationality:egyptian##2
3. Nationality:nigerian is on the right of Nationality:mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | mexican | nigerian | egyptian | chinese |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: pineapple, tomato, asparagus, lettuce
1. Food:pineapple is on the left of Food:lettuce##1
2. Food:tomato is in an odd position##4
3. Food:tomato is on the left or right of Food:pineapple##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | tomato | pineapple | lettuce | asparagus |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: horror, documentary, romance, satire
1. Movie-Genre:satire is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:horror##3
2. Movie-Genre:horror is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:romance is between Movie-Genre:satire and Movie-Genre:documentary##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | satire | romance | documentary |

