.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: watermelon, cabbage, apple, kale
1. Food:cabbage == Food:cabbage##1
2. Food:kale is on the left or right of Food:apple##3
3. Food:apple is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:watermelon is in an even position##4
5. Food:kale is on the left of Food:cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | apple | kale | cabbage | watermelon |

